Upload photos of the items you want to put on the model. Step 1. Read the guidelines: - Crop the photo to remove anything that is not the clothing item. - There must be no human or mannequin heads in the image. - Higher resolution gives better results. - Complex metallic hardware may not be rendered perfectly. - Zippers may require more attempts to look correct. Step 2. Choose the type of your photo: - Clothing only (lying or hanging) - On a person (no face, minimum distractions) - On a mannequin (no mannequin head) Step 3. Upload a photo of one or several items. Important: each uploaded photo counts as a separate item.
